headline: Integra LifeSciences, Evolent Health, Incyte, iRhythm, and Clover Health Stocks Trade Up, What You Need To Know
summary: A number of stocks jumped in the afternoon session after a report revealed that the White House plans to pitch a two-year extension of Obamacare subsidies.
